# The built .dotm lives in Word's STARTUP folder (the copy Word actually loads),
# NOT in this repo. src/ is the source; build/Import-Macros.ps1 rebuilds the
# STARTUP copy on every pull. Nothing of value lives only in the .dotm: the form
# is kept in src/ as frmSuggest.frm + .frx (run Export-Macros once).
My_Macros.dotm

# VBE export noise
*.frx.bak
~$*
